Facilyn: Now we look ahead: what must your future resource base be like to sustain that quality of life?

Facilyn: There are two elements to it. The first is people.

Facilyn: People judge you by your behaviour, not your slogans. Describe how you need to show up to keep the support of those in your resource base — customers, clients, suppliers, family, friends, anyone you rely on.

